text: The 1926 Maryland gubernatorial election was held on November 2, 1926. Incumbent Democrat Albert Ritchie defeated Republican nominee Addison E. Mullikin with 57.93% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== Major party candidates *Albert Ritchie, Democratic *Addison E. Mullikin, Republican Other candidates *P. G'ustave Dill, Socialist ===Results=== ==References== 1926 Maryland Gubernatorial
title: 1926 Maryland gubernatorial election
